OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FIreland's premier is marking 250 years
OL,8,Fof United States independence during a
OL,9,Fvisit to Philadelphia.
OL,11,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin's visit to
OL,12,Fthe Pennsylvanian city comes as part
OL,13,Fof the annual visit by Ireland's
OL,14,Fleader to the US for St Patrick's Day,
OL,15,Fwhich will include a meeting with
OL,16,FPresident Donald Trump at the White
OL,17,FHouse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
