FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FThis year's visit has been described
OL,8,Fby the Taoiseach's office as very
OL,9,Fspecial as the US celebrates 250 years
OL,10,Fsince the signing of the Declaration
OL,11,Fof Independence.
OL,13,FMr Martin celebrated Irish athletes,
OL,14,Fas well as making a brief stop-off at
OL,15,Fthe steps of the Philadelphia Museum
OL,16,Fof Art made famous by the Rocky films.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FHe met athletes studying at Villanova
OL,8,FUniversity as part of the Irish
OL,9,FPipeline athletics programme which has
OL,10,Fshaped 13 Irish Olympians including
OL,11,FSonia O'Sullivan, Eamonn Coghlan and
OL,12,FRonnie Delaney, the last Irish athlete
OL,13,Fto win gold on the track at the
OL,14,FOlympics in 1956.
OL,16,FEarlier, the Taoiseach laid a wreath
OL,17,Fat the Irish Memorial dedicated to the
OL,18,Fmore than one million Irish who died
OL,19,Fin the famine, as well as the millions
OL,20,Fof migrants who made the US their home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FHe hailed the sculpture for telling
OL,8,Fthe traumatic stories of those who
OL,9,Fdied during the famine from 1845-52,
OL,10,Fthose who endured traumatic journeys
OL,11,Ffor a new life and contributed towards
OL,12,Fthe building of the United States.
OL,14,F"Delighted to be here in Philadelphia,
OL,15,Fthe birthplace of the Republic," he
OL,16,Ftold reporters in Philadelphia.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
