PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,F"Today will be a day focused on that
OL,8,Fcontribution of the Irish, beginning
OL,9,Fhere laying a wreath at this beautiful
OL,10,Fmemorial which remembers the one
OL,11,Fmillion people who died during the
OL,12,FIrish famine, a million more who
OL,13,Femigrated and many more who were
OL,14,Flooked after by American hosts at that
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,17,FLater, the Taoiseach will attend the
OL,18,F255th Annual Gala of the Friendly Sons
OL,19,Fand Daughters of Saint Patrick with
OL,20,F400 business and community leaders
OL,21,Ffrom Philadelphia.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
