OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FIt was founded in 1771 by Cork man
OL,8,FStephen Moylan, a celebrated general
OL,9,Fin the American Revolution, George
OL,10,FWashington's aide de camp and the man
OL,11,Fsaid to be responsible for the first
OL,12,Fwritten record of the phrase The
OL,13,FUnited States of America.
OL,15,F"That, in many ways, illustrates the
OL,16,Fdepth and fundamental nature of the
OL,17,FIrish-American relationship,
OL,18,Fparticularly in the context of the
OL,19,Fdeclaration of American independence,"
OL,20,FMr Martin said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
