CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FOn Sunday, Mr Martin will attend the
OL,8,FPhiladelphia St Patrick's Day Parade
OL,9,Fand lay a wreath at the statue of
OL,10,FCommodore John Barry.
OL,12,FThe visit to Philadelphia comes at the
OL,13,Fstart of the Taoiseach's annual visit
OL,14,Fto the United States for St Patrick's
OL,15,FDay.
OL,17,FHe is set to travel on to Washington
OL,18,FDC for the traditional celebrations
OL,19,Ffor Ireland's national holiday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
