PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773551082
OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FHis itinerary includes a bilateral
OL,8,Fmeeting with Mr Trump in the Oval
OL,9,FOffice on Tuesday.
OL,11,FLast year's meeting saw the US
OL,12,Fpresident take questions from
OL,13,Freporters for almost an hour.
OL,15,FThe Irish Government said the
OL,16,Fdiscussions will cover a range of
OL,17,Fissues, including the "deep ties"
OL,18,Fbetween the two countries.
OL,26,@yD@WOUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
