OL,3,CIrish premier marking 250 years of US
OL,4,Cindependence during visit to
OL,5,CPhiladelpia
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's deputy First
OL,8,FMinister Emma Little-Pengelly said she
OL,9,Fwould be going to Washington to engage
OL,10,Fwith the president, while First
OL,11,FMinister Michelle O'Neill and other
OL,12,FSinn Fein politicians are boycotting
OL,13,Fthe White House.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
